**Another Solution:**&lt;br&gt;

If you have several modules in your android project, please make sure you have added the below config to every module that uses the kotlin:&lt;br&gt;

**Step(1)- Project build.gradle:&lt;br&gt;**
```
// Project build.gradle file.
